---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Our History - Formerly Sears Cleaning | Empire Cleaning Group"
  description="Discover the history of Empire Cleaning Group, formerly a Sears Cleaning partner for over 15 years in Montreal, Laval, and South Shore."
>
  <div class="page-header bg-gradient-premium">
    <div class="container text-center fade-in-section">
      <span class="sub-title">A Tradition of Excellence</span>
      <h1 class="text-gradient">Our History</h1>
      <p class="lead-text">
        Continuity of professional cleaning expertise in Montreal, South Shore,
        and North Shore.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="history-layout">
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div class="history-content fade-in-section">
          <!-- PREMIUM LEGACY BADGE (ENHANCED) -->
          <div class="legacy-highlight-container">
            <div class="legacy-badge-large">
              <span class="legacy-icon">✨</span>
              <span class="legacy-text"
                >Formerly <strong>Sears Cleaning</strong></span
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="section-title">Official partner for over 15 years</h2>

          <p class="text-content">
            For over 15 years, our team was the official professional cleaning
            partner for <strong>Sears Cleaning</strong> in Montreal, on the South
            Shore, and North Shore. Thousands of residential and commercial clients
            trusted us for carpet cleaning, furniture cleaning, sofa, couch, sectional
            cleaning, wool rugs, area rugs, stair cleaning, and mattresses.
          </p>

          <p class="text-content">
            If you have done business with Sears Cleaning in Montreal, on the
            South Shore, or North Shore, chances are it was **our team that
            intervened at your home**. It is the same technicians, the same
            proven methods, and the same professional rigor that built Sears'
            reputation in the region.
          </p>

          <hr class="separator" />

          <h3>An evolution towards excellence</h3>
          <p class="text-content">
            Today, under the name **Empire Cleaning Group**, we continue this
            tradition of excellence in professional cleaning in Montreal, on the
            South Shore, and North Shore, while maintaining high standards,
            recognized customer service, and field expertise acquired over the
            years.
          </p>
          <p class="text-content">
            We now add **even higher performance steam cleaning technologies**,
            modern truck-mount units, and new generation ecological products.
          </p>

          <div class="info-box">
            <h4>Areas Served</h4>
            <p>
              Our company relies on real and continuous experience in
              residential and commercial cleaning, developed with a loyal and
              demanding clientele in Montreal, on the South Shore, and North
              Shore, including sectors like:
            </p>
            <ul class="locations-list">
              <li>Longueuil</li>
              <li>Brossard</li>
              <li>Saint-Hubert</li>
              <li>Boucherville</li>
              <li>Montreal</li>
              <li>Laval and surroundings</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <p class="closing-statement">
            Choosing **Empire Cleaning Group** means choosing the continuity of
            a recognized service, the stability of an experienced team, and the
            peace of mind of entrusting your furniture and carpets to
            professionals who have already earned the trust of thousands of
            clients in the region.
          </p>

          <p
            style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: 1.5rem;"
          >
            If you trusted Sears Cleaning, you can trust Empire Cleaning Group
            today.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-history">
            <a href="/en/equipe" class="btn btn-secondary">Meet our team</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Request an estimate</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar / Visuals -->
        <div class="history-visuals fade-in-section delay-100">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="number">15+</span>
            <span class="label">Years Sears Partner</span>
          </div>

          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="number">100%</span>
            <span class="label">Satisfaction Guaranteed</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Placeholder for visual -->
          <div
            class="history-img"
            style="margin-top:2rem; overflow:hidden; border-radius:8px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-subtle);"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/services/services-1.webp"
              alt="Techniciens Groupe Nettoyage Empire"
              style="width:100%; height:auto; display:block;"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    /* Using global utility .bg-gradient-premium via class, but adding fallback padding */
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .sub-title {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .history-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
  }

  .highlight-badge {
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .text-content {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .separator {
    border: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: #eee;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .info-box {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .info-box h4 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .locations-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .locations-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .locations-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    color: var(--color-accent);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }

  .closing-statement {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #333;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .cta-history {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  }

  .stat-card .number {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-card .label {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 5px;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .history-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    .cta-history {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }

  /* --- PREMIUM LEGACY BADGE STYLES --- */
  .legacy-highlight-container {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start; /* Aligned left like text */
  }

  .legacy-badge-large {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      #f0f7ff 0%,
      #e6f0ff 100%
    ); /* Light Blue Tint */
    border: 2px solid #003399; /* Sears Blue Border */
    padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 153, 0.15);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .legacy-badge-large::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8),
      transparent
    );
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    animation: shine 6s infinite;
  }

  .legacy-badge-large:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 51, 153, 0.25);
  }

  .legacy-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1));
  }

  .legacy-text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: #0a2342; /* Dark Blue */
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .legacy-text strong {
    color: #003399; /* Sears Blue */
    font-weight: 800;
    display: block; /* Stack on mobile if needed, or inline */
  }

  @keyframes shine {
    0% {
      transform: translateX(-100%);
    }
    20% {
      transform: translateX(100%);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateX(100%);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legacy-badge-large {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .legacy-text {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .legacy-text strong {
      display: inline;
    }
  }
</style>
